text.tspan: Heal from scratched: 2 + 1dF - ρ days must pass. ρ is included when a related skill
(e.g. Wound Care) is applied, and uses D = -1.
[bp] is hurt: -1 to actions that rely on [bp]
Heal from hurt: 4 + 2dF - ρ days must pass. ρ is included when a related skill
(e.g. Wound Care) is applied, and uses D = 0.
[bp] is incapacitated: -3 to actions that rely on [bp]
Heal from incapacitated: 6 + 3dF - ρ days must pass. ρ is included when a related skill
(e.g. Wound Care) is applied, and uses D = 1.
Extenuous circumstances: There's no way out of this, unless...
